        ☐ <stdlib.h> → ../lib/stdlib.h
        ☐ <string.h> → ../lib/string.h
        ☐ <ctype.h>  → ../lib/ctype.h
    ☐ Adapter I/O
        ☐ printf() → transparent via mini libc
        ☐ scanf() / fgets() → readline() du terminal
        ☐ read_file.c → vfs_open / vfs_read

